Hello, world! &#x1f44b;
I am currently a PhD candidate at the University of Antwerp, where I develop numerical methods for atom probe tomography. This lets us see the atom-by-atom composition of a sample in 3D! &#x1f52c; For my efforts thus far I was awarded a Student Scholar Award at the Microscopy and Microanalysis Conference 2024. &#x1f3c6;
Before my PhD I worked at the German Aerospace Center (DLR), where I developed geometric methods for the design of turbine blade cooling structures.
